> Staying in the shadows. She watched this new creature. By the looks
of it, 
> they were similar to her, a mix of organic & cybernetic. 
> 
> 'Trans-organics!' she thought. Was this a horrible experiment by the
Quints? 
> They attempted this long ago.  
> 
> "You were very poor in stealth." She called out in a feline femme
voice, with 
> a slight deep sophistication to it. "Are you Autobot or Decepticon?
Or are 
> you a pathetic Transorganic experiment created by the Quints?" 
> 
> She stayed in the shadows, out of sight... for now. Waiting to see
who this 
> newcomer was & what they were. Her questions were mounting.

Melchana focused her optics and saw vaguely the feline form in the
dark. Then she started laughing out loud.

Melchana: Autobots? Decepticons? Quintesson expirement? Oh boy! You
are funny! Me and all the new rulers of this planet have nothing to do
with any of those!

She walked a little closer, but still at a good range.

Melchana: I'm Melchana. A Tripredacus. I'm not organic, even partly,
but my body is composed of nanites that imitate organic matter... only
better. As for you... we detected you and we wanted to see what you
were. What are you?
